Taikai Example Segment
======================

This is a deterministic placeholder payload that mimics a CMAF fragment for the
Taikai publisher sample. The bytes are intentionally small so the example can
run on developer laptops without dedicated media assets.

Frame Index,PTS(us),Duration(us),Notes
0,3600000,200000,"synthetic frame"
1,3800000,200000,"synthetic frame"
2,4000000,200000,"synthetic frame"
3,4200000,200000,"synthetic frame"

End of sample payload.

